comment: Adams (OKC) and Jordan (LAC) make incidental contact with one another away from the ball.
Adams (LAC) makes contact with Jordan's (LAC) body during his shot attempt.
Paul (LAC) and Durant (OKC) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Westbrook (OKC) lifts his pivot foot, but does not return it to the floor before losing control of the ball.
Roberson (OKC) makes contact with Jordan's (LAC) arm and body during rebounding that affects his tip-in shot attempt.
Foye (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position on the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Crawford (LAC).
Paul (LAC) makes incidental contact with Westbrook (OKC) that does not affect his FOM away from the ball.
Johnson (LAC) makes contact with Durant's (OKC) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ibaka (OKC) and Jordan (LAC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Paul (LAC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Westbrook's (OKC) jump shot attempt. Any contact on the play is initiated by Westbrook.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Ibaka (OKC) prior to going OOB was confirmed.
Waiters (OKC) commits a take foul on Redick (LAC).
